[center][b][i]What is ZodiacsReign?[/i] [b][font=Verdana]ZodiacsReign is a RSPS helper containing mostly required programs and files to make your RSPS coding and playing more proficient and easy, Zodiacsreign has been around for almost 2 years and I've been updating for a very long time. In "ZodiacsReign Packages" you will find Tools, Id List , Essentials to make your private server experience a better one.[/b][/center]
[center][b][i] In the new ZodiacsReign 8.0, I've added alot more tools and a few more list to help you out, This is i have to admit not a great one like the past ones.[/b][/i][/center] [Center][size=20pt]Download Link~[/size] http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?zemggxwtyn1 [b]2.55mb[/b] [img]http://www.mediafire.com/free-file-hosting/mediafire-swoosh.gif[/img] [img]http://i30.tinypic.com/2ztikh0.jpg[/img][/center]
[Center][i][size=11pt][b]Features[/b][/center] [center] [b][size=12pt]317 List[/b] [list] [color=orange][list][li]317 Item List[/li] [li]317 NPC List[/li] [li]317 Interface List[/li] [li]317 Graphics List[/li] [li]317 Object List[/li] [li]317 Emote List [/li] [li]317 Coordinate List [/li] [li]317 Animation List [/li] [li]And More[/li][/list]
[b][size=12pt][color=green]508 List[/b] [list][li]508 Interface List[/li] [li]508 NPC List [/li] [li]508 Object List[/li] [li]508 Item List[/li] [li]508 Graphics List[/li] [li]508 Hair & Clothes Color List[/li] [li]508 Emotes List[/li] [li]508 Sounds List [/li][/list]
[b][size=12pt][color=blue]Tools[/b] [list][li]Eleclions Server Rebooter[/li] [li]Meiscooldudes Shopmaker & Server Runetime Manager[/li] [li]Hypercam Set-Up[/li] [li]Basic Command Generator[/li] [li]Voule's Auto-Restarter[/li] [li]Voule's Command Generator [/li] [li]Voule's Auto-spawn Generator[/li] [li]Backup Tool[/li] [li]Character Editor[/li] [li]Runescape Windows Client[/li] [li]WinterLove Server[/li] [li]Brand new Shop-Maker[/li] [li]Sprite-Maker[/li] [li]Moparscape Client[/li] [li]Server Item Clearer[/li] [li]525 Item List[/li] [li]Auto-typer & Auto-clicker[/li] [li]And More[/li] [li]More tools then before![/li] [/list]
